    "element_subtype": "standard-indented",
    "content": "<strong>Guiding Principles in Choosing the Location</strong>&mdash;In choosing a home, God would have us consider, first of all, the moral and religious influences that will surround us and our families.<sup class=\"chapterendnote\"><a class=\"chapterendnote\">1<span class=\"chapterendnote\"><span class=\"egwlink egwlink_book\" title=\"PP 169.1\" data-link=\"84.688\">Patriarchs and Prophets, 169</span>.</span></a></sup>",
