    "element_type": "p",
    "element_subtype": "standard-indented",
    "content": "The gospel ... teaches us to estimate things at their true value, and to give the most effort to the things of greatest worth&mdash;the things that will endure. This lesson is needed by those upon whom rests the responsibility of selecting a home. They should not allow themselves to be diverted from the highest aim....",
